### =========================
### USER API


### Get all users
GET http://localhost:4000/user-api/users


### Get user by MongoDB ObjectId
GET http://localhost:4000/user-api/users/697dbc3d50a191a58fbfeb7b


### Create new user
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "matthew",
  "password": "matthew",
  "age": 21
}


### Update user by ObjectId
PUT http://localhost:4000/user-api/users/697dbc3d50a191a58fbfeb7b
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "matthew",
  "password": "matthew",
  "age": 22
}


### Delete user by ObjectId
DELETE http://localhost:4000/user-api/users/697dbc3d50a191a58fbfeb7b



### Protected route (requires login first)
GET http://localhost:4000/user-api/test


